<section class="policy">
    <div class="container" style="padding: 100px;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h1 class="policy-title">Purchase & Payment Policy</h1>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    At Timeless Jewelry, we aim to make your shopping experience seamless and secure. Below are the terms and guidelines for purchasing and payment on our website.
                </p>
                <h3 class="sub-policy-title">Accepted Payment Methods</h3>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>We accept the following payment methods:</li>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Credit and Debit Cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express).</li>
                            <li>Bank Transfers (available for select regions).</li>
                            <li>Digital Wallets.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <li>All payments are processed securely to ensure the safety of your personal information.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <h3 class="sub-policy-title">Order Confirmation</h3>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Once your payment is successfully processed, you will receive an order confirmation email with your order details.</li>
                        <li>If you do not receive a confirmation email, please check your spam/junk folder or contact us at <strong>customer.service@timelessjewelry.com</strong>.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <h3 class="sub-policy-title">Pricing and Currency</h3>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>All prices are listed in <strong>US dollar</strong>. For international customers, the total amount will be converted to your local currency by your bank or payment provider.</li>
                        <li>Taxes, duties, and additional fees (if applicable) will be calculated at checkout and included in your total.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <h3 class="sub-policy-title">Installment Payments</h3>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>We offer flexible installment payment options for eligible orders. Please check the "Installments" option during checkout for more details.</li>
                        <li>Failure to complete installment payments as agreed may result in cancellation or additional fees.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <h3 class="sub-policy-title">Failed or Declined Payments</h3>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>If your payment is declined, please verify your payment details and try again.</li>
                        <li>For assistance, contact your bank or our customer service team at <strong>customer.service@timelessjewelry.com</strong>.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <h3 class="sub-policy-title">Secure Transactions</h3>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>We use industry-standard encryption to protect your payment information during transactions.</li>
                        <li>Your privacy and security are our priority. Please review our <a href="privacy.html" class="policy-link">Privacy Policy</a> for more details.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p class="policy-content">
                    If you have any questions about our purchase and payment policy, feel free to contact us at <strong>customer.service@timelessjewelry.com</strong>. Weâ€™re here to help make your shopping experience easy and enjoyable!
                </p>
